424
00:48:35,960 --> 00:48:38,820
Don't you care about anyone else?

425
00:48:38,820 --> 00:48:41,640
Why are you only thinking about your own hurt?

426
00:48:53,300 --> 00:48:58,710
Yes. I'm Jang Yi Hyeon's guardian.

427
00:49:00,150 --> 00:49:05,000
